metadata.name: Z
metadata.description:
The letter "Z" is a unique art from the "Living Alphabet" collection.

All letters in the collection are unique, they have many details that make them a special part of a large living organism.

The owner of the letter will have access to unlock the Luma Matte content - a mask that will allow him to cut this letter from the video and use it without a background.

---///---

2160x2160 / 25 fps / Loop
